'States' we care about in this game

- total amount of unfound matches (status display to user)
- time since start (SDTU)
- number of non-matches (SDTU)
- win game
- restart game

For Tiles
- has this tile been matched
	if yes = show
	if no = flip back over

	OR
	if match == show + disable click


- has the tile been clicked
- how many tiles have been clicked (true)
	- limit clicks to 3